q2.value:
In this correlational study we expect that:

H1: Attitudes towards calling a helpline are significantly associated with intentions to call a helpline, in men and women who are victimized in different sex and same-sex relationships;

H2: Attitudes towards calling a helpline will be a significant predictor of intentions to call a helpline in men and women who are victimized in different sex and same-sex relationships;

H3: Gender role conflict in victimized men will be negatively associated with attitudes towards calling a helpline;

H4: Gender role conflict in victimized men will be negatively associated with intentions to call a helpline;

